00:42:21.020 --> 00:42:23.220
We just need to do some taping.

00:42:23.220 --> 00:42:25.120
This is the truncated
tetrahedron.

00:42:25.120 --> 00:42:28.290
It's got four triangles,
four hexagons.

00:42:28.290 --> 00:42:29.700
So we've already
made-- last time

00:42:29.700 --> 00:42:31.025
