by themselves.

00:42:40.700 --> 00:42:44.747
We've got enough hypars
to make the four hexagons,

00:42:44.747 --> 00:42:46.580
and then we just need
to tape them together,

00:42:46.580 --> 00:42:49.010
and we will get the
truncated tetrahedron.

